item.title: Help with textures
item.dc:creator: @primadude Primadude
item.description:
@primadude wrote:

The problem you have isn’t related to the object textures; it’s related to the object Models. You have replaced an already existing model with the model of whatever the fences or other models show up as. If you want to fix it, download and use a clean cache that hasn’t got any models overwritten/added.
